Basic knowledge on Oracle Fusion Middleware (e.g. WebLogic)
Basic knowledge of Cloud (OCI, AWS or AZURE)
Knowledge on Enterprise Manager
In-depth knowledge of Oracle database technologies and architecture

Familiarity with AWS services (Aurora, RDS, EC2, S3, etc.) and cloud database management practices.
Experience with query tuning tools such as pg_stat_statements and EXPLAIN for query analysis.
Conceptual knowledge of Terraform
Good understanding on DNS, TCP/IP protocols.
Exposure to security concepts / best practices; Understanding on IPsec, VPN, Load Balancing, Iperf, MTR, Routing Protocols, SSH, Network
